Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,La Li Ho!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už si vyzdravel?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej! Už je mi dobre.
