Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.76,0:02:53.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mimochodom, kde je Hiro?
