Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Choď domov a pospi si.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.97,0:03:07.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Viete, to je...
