Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Sh-Shindo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja... viem, že sme konečne...
