Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A chcem sa za to ospravedlniť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie toto!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.53,0:03:28.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toto som myslel, toto!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A toto! A ešte toto!
