Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.47,0:03:41.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nežartuj prosím, Shindo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.41,0:03:43.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to má znamenať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja... končím s Bad Luck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.11,0:03:52.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Hiro a Fujisaku s tým nič nemajú.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.99,0:03:55.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to moja vina,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ak si nájdete nového speváka...
