Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie viac ako desiatimi slovami.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.03,0:04:08.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čoskoro sa dozviete. A navyše...
