Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stratím sa z tvojho života.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.18,0:09:24.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Opustíš ma,\Naj keď som sa takto prezliekol?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je hlavný dôvod.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože som chlap?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vymenil som si aj spodky! Oholil nohy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kedy som povedal,\Nže ťa nenávidím, lebo si muž?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.47,0:09:46.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inak by som ti nevravel,\Nže budem tvojím milencom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, prečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK, hotovo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.74,0:10:28.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nahrávanie skončilo, gratulujem!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.31,0:10:29.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo! Bravo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konečne nám to vyšlo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka! Všetkým vám ďakujem!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale no tak, len sme začali,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dúfam, že nebudeš chcieť opäť skončiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Presne! Vodca do toho musí ísť s nami!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.69,0:10:43.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jasnačka!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.79,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, beriem ťa za slovo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.46,0:10:49.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože som sa vzdal Yukiho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.14,0:10:56.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už nebudem prežívať depresie...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a vsústredím sa na prácu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.08,0:11:03.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Touto cestou aspoň nebudem Yukimu na obtiaž.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.92,0:11:13.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takmer nič o ňom nevieš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pravda.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dôvod, prečo je vždy\Ntak chladný a bezcitný...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...je ten, že nikomu nechce\Nukázať jeho skutočné ja.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.70,0:11:29.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokážem milovať Yukiho,\Nktorého nepoznám?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.48,0:11:36.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ano, spolupracovali sme predsa\Ndlhý čas, pani Kaoruko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dúfam, že naše dobré vzťahy\Nbudú trvať naďalej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}"Kto je Yuki?!\NBad Luck (Shindo Shuichi)\NExkluzívne vyznanie!!"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}"Kto je Yuki?!\NBad Luck (Shindo Shuichi)\NExkluzívne vyznanie!!"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, ozvem sa vám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.42,0:11:44.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}"Kto je Yuki?!\NBad Luck (Shindo Shuichi)\NExkluzívne vyznanie!!"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haló? Tu je Seguchi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.53,0:11:59.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Potreboval by som od vás jednu láskavosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa,\Nže je to osobná záležitosť, ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa,\Nže je to osobná záležitosť, ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte jedno!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme ešte niekam!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.51,0:12:06.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslíš "Poďme ešte niekam".\NSi rozbitý.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslíš "Poďme ešte niekam".\NSi rozbitý.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.48,0:12:14.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Yuki dokáže vypiť 4 flaše\Na byť úplne triezvy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.32,0:12:16.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, hej, ty ožralo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.79,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kto je ožralý?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.29,0:12:21.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boli sme len v jednom podniku...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.16,0:12:22.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo ti je?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.16,0:12:23.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Budem vracať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.17,0:12:33.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počuj...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,vážne si sa vzdal Yukiho?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Úplne vážne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Úplne smrtelne vážne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.08,0:12:48.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň sa tak pýtať, ty sviniar!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.99,0:12:51.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa musíš pýtať\Nmilión-krát na tú istú vec.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak prečo si potom prišiel sem...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čakala som na vás.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kedy to chodíte domov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.73,0:13:05.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrý večer, Nakano.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti, že si mi vtedy pomohol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, to je v poriadku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.84,0:13:14.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dobré správy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vravel, že sa vzdá Yukiho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.62,0:13:22.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Úplne vážne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.79,0:13:25.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Úplne smrtelne vážne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vravím predsa, že...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zmýlila som sa v tebe, Shindo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.03,0:13:37.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslela som, že tvoj vzťah\Nk Eirimu bude pevnejší.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale na tom už nezáleží.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.57,0:13:44.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Včera som prijala jeho ponuku na sobáš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Žartuješ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.04,0:13:51.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoj vzťah s Eirim je týmto u konca.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak nič neurobíš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nezahrávaj sa so mnou,\Nčo to má znamenať!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už ho nezaujímam ja,\Ntak si našiel niekoho iného?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To mu neodpustím!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.32,0:14:30.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-ty hlupák!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.59,0:14:37.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hral si sa mnou dokým ťa to bavilo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a potom zmizneš a nájdeš si nevestu?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.56,0:14:44.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zmizni! Zmizni!\NSkutočne sa rozhodol zmiznúť?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočný Yuki...\NA Yuki, ktorého som poznal...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trápiť sa kvôli takej hlúposti...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.32,0:15:02.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Najväčší hlupák tu som ja!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.79,0:15:06.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To ti povedala Ayaka?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.36,0:15:13.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo ti povedala?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je jedno!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poď Shuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.97,0:15:24.57,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bude to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bude to tvoja posledná šanca.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.03,0:15:54.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oznámil som našému božstvu,\Nže budeš mať konečne rodinu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.01,0:16:01.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už dlho som nevidel Ayaku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale počul som,\Nže z nej vyrástla nádherná dáma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.57,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nádnerná dáma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.95,0:16:09.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pri pohľade na jej prsia\Nvyzerá ako dieťa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.46,0:16:14.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Prsia?! Ty jeden?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.96,0:16:15.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otec, ukľudni sa! Ukľudni sa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.69,0:16:16.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otec, ukľudni sa! Ukľudni sa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, a kde je naša mladá dáma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.13,0:16:24.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuha ju zachvíľku privezie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte mi to zdržanie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už je tu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.14,0:16:34.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pozvi ju prosím dnu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrite, už je pripravená.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka, prosím!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ano, prepáčte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.43,0:16:57.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Túžila som ťa znovu vidieť, Eiri.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.94,0:17:09.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta školácka uniforma vyzerala lepšie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je všetko?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.75,0:17:16.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nechceš mi niečo povedať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.19,0:17:20.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten, kto mi chce niečo povedať,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,si predsa ty, nie?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, chcem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja... prišiel som na to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...že ťa milujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bez ohľadu na to, aký si,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bez ohľadu na tvoju minulosť,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki je stále Yuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.82,0:17:53.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem žiť s tým,\Nže o tebe nič neviem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.66,0:18:00.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prezraď mi prosím všetko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zabil som človeka.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.64,0:18:14.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keď mi bolo 16, v meste kde som žil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.51,0:18:19.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Úmyselne som ho zabil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spokojný?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je moja minulosť,\Nktorú si túžil poznať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.43,0:18:39.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pred chvíľou si povedal,\Nže ma miluješ.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.74,0:18:45.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokážeš to povedať i teraz?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preskočilo ti?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samozrejme, že viem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.79,0:18:58.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Na minulosti nezáleží?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.39,0:19:03.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš sa predomnou skrývať,\Nale už je neskoro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.09,0:19:07.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už mi neutečieš!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.70,0:19:14.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Máš ešte guráž\Noženiť sa s niekym iným?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.32,0:19:27.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To si píš, že hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo za čo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.09,0:19:32.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dosť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vráť sa domov, Shuichi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Práve si ma oslovil Shuichi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mojím menom...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.30,0:19:47.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, hej, Yuki, Yuki, práve si ma\Noslovil mojím prvým menom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.27,0:19:50.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, povedz to znovu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.37,0:19:54.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sme predsa milenci, nie?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ukľudni sa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Súhlasíš s tým?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.09,0:20:06.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Schválne si mu to povedala, Ayaka...
