Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.11,0:20:46.41,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nigiyaka na hitogomi ni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.85,0:20:51.15,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The murmured words melt away
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.85,0:20:51.15,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokeru tsubuyaki ga
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.52,0:20:55.65,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scattered at my feet
