Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.76,0:21:06.27,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wander aimlessly
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.76,0:21:06.27,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi aruku
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.27,0:21:09.86,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the brilliant lights of the town
