Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.57,0:21:49.17,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A faint silhouette that guides me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.57,0:21:49.17,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boku o michibiku kasuka na shiruetto
